1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:58,120 --> 00:01:04,629
[We Are Young]

3
00:01:04,810 --> 00:01:07,530
[Episode 39]

4
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:11,590
Anti-fans, double agents,
imitation products, account suspension,

5
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:13,650
and now, stealing Mr Five's designs?

6
00:01:14,610 --> 00:01:17,260
Aren't you despicable?

7
00:01:19,410 --> 00:01:21,660
I met her once before this.

8
00:01:22,630 --> 00:01:25,620
Actually, she longs for this very much.

9
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,430
I once mentioned to you

10
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:30,030
and urged you on.

11
00:01:30,670 --> 00:01:32,870
It's a pity that it didn't materialise.

12
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,979
Now I want to make up for it.

13
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:39,850
I was hoping you'd
be excited to hear this.

14
00:01:40,610 --> 00:01:41,700
Looks like

15
00:01:41,789 --> 00:01:42,979
it's hopeless now.

16
00:01:45,250 --> 00:01:46,700
I don't mind.

17
00:01:47,220 --> 00:01:48,590
You can be angry, too.

18
00:01:48,670 --> 00:01:50,520
It's simply ridiculous.

19
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:53,170
I'd never have expected you

20
00:01:53,259 --> 00:01:55,100
to steal someone's ideas

21
00:01:55,190 --> 00:01:56,950
and use it to justify yourself.

22
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:05,460
My work here is done.

23
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:24,300
[Moe Tea]

24
00:02:24,980 --> 00:02:26,570
[I have conclusive evidence]

25
00:02:26,570 --> 00:02:29,060
[that you sent us the imitation products
on Singles' Day.]

26
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:31,000
[I'd never have expected you]

27
00:02:31,090 --> 00:02:33,420
[to steal someone's ideas...]

28
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:38,390
[Hello.]

29
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,700
[Hello, please speak up.]

30
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:47,410
Hello, I want to report
on an unfair competition.

31
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:49,000
The company involved

32
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,640
is Cloud Live.

33
00:02:51,210 --> 00:02:52,090
[B2]

34
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:57,420
[It's such a white shirt skirt.]

35
00:02:57,510 --> 00:02:58,410
[And,]

36
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,710
[it has a nice bow-knot design.]

37
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,740
Its cuffs are hollow.

38
00:03:02,820 --> 00:03:03,970
Just take a look.

39
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:05,290
[Even...]

40
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,990
[Cloud Live,
Live streaming account is suspended]

41
00:03:06,990 --> 00:03:08,060
What's going on?

42
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,410
Go check it out.

43
00:03:10,250 --> 00:03:11,350
What happened?

44
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,710
I have no idea.

45
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:14,160
It's suspended.

46
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:15,350
Is it suspended?

47
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,220
It suddenly happened.

48
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:18,630
Yes, indeed.

49
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:28,710
Everyone, gather around.

50
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:29,920
Just calm yourselves down.

51
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,720
Listen to me.

52
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:33,590
It was unexpected.

53
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,530
I just knew about it.

54
00:03:35,810 --> 00:03:37,960
There's something more serious.

55
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,430
Double 12 is coming up.

56
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,930
Then there's the Lantern Festival,

57
00:03:40,930 --> 00:03:43,650
and a series of promotional
events afterward.

58
00:03:44,250 --> 00:03:46,640
We mustn't rest on our laurels.

59
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:48,670
I'll get us a temporary platform.

60
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:51,240
I believe the suspension won't be long.

61
00:03:51,329 --> 00:03:53,530
I heard such suspensions usually last

62
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:54,790
at least three months.

63
00:03:54,790 --> 00:03:56,050
Are we going to be fine?

64
00:03:56,050 --> 00:03:58,160
Wen Wen, you're scaring everyone.

65
00:03:58,810 --> 00:04:00,000
Listen.

66
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:02,160
When we first started,

67
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,140
didn't I fulfill all my promises

68
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:06,350
that I made to you all?

69
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,720
Now we're having a little trouble,

70
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:10,430
we can't just back out from it, right?

71
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:12,790
We can't know for sure
what's going to happen next.

72
00:04:12,790 --> 00:04:14,600
Three months isn't too long.

73
00:04:14,690 --> 00:04:17,019
And we'll keep on
waiting during this time.

74
00:04:17,019 --> 00:04:19,480
Waiting without salary
for three month is

75
00:04:19,570 --> 00:04:20,850
unacceptable.

76
00:04:22,410 --> 00:04:23,600
During this time,

77
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,270
you'll still get your salary.

78
00:04:25,090 --> 00:04:29,980
[Shapowei Art Zone]

79
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:30,540
Can't you two just talk it over?

80
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:31,940
Just talk to him.

81
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:39,730
Mao.

82
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,890
Well,

83
00:04:43,980 --> 00:04:46,270
Mr Five wants to talk to you.

84
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:49,909
You two should just talk it over.

85
00:04:49,909 --> 00:04:50,890
Start talking to each other.

86
00:04:50,890 --> 00:04:53,260
I have something urgent in hand.

87
00:04:53,350 --> 00:04:55,230
I'm very busy.

88
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,510
-Go ahead.
-Xi XI.

89
00:04:56,590 --> 00:04:57,870
Just go.

90
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:13,620
Well,

91
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:16,920
I'm going to do a live stream
with Jiang Zhe Yang.

92
00:05:16,970 --> 00:05:19,030
Project Vine is back on track.

93
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:24,330
Are you angry with me?

94
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:25,960
I'm sorry.

95
00:05:37,230 --> 00:05:39,190
I was too engrossed in my work

96
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,770
that I neglected your feelings.

97
00:05:40,770 --> 00:05:41,770
I was foolish

98
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:42,890
and careless, too.

99
00:05:42,890 --> 00:05:44,770
Just let it out on me.

100
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:46,490
Don't be angry.

101
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:54,320
It's passed.

102
00:06:01,490 --> 00:06:02,810
I'm sorry.

103
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:10,600
It's simply impossible to do that.

104
00:06:09,110 --> 00:06:12,580
[Resignation Letter]

105
00:06:15,210 --> 00:06:17,810
I've something urgent in
hand. Call you later.

106
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:27,200
Xiao Xiao.

107
00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:29,920
Why the resignation at this time?

108
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:32,409
You're my head broadcaster.

109
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:34,220
Our 40 percent of viewership

110
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:36,470
comes from you. If you go now,

111
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,560
what will happen to
the rest of the company?

112
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:39,840
Mr Chen.

113
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,840
The suspension is serious.

114
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:44,260
We won't be unsuspended for quite a while.

115
00:06:44,610 --> 00:06:46,020
No jobs in three month,

116
00:06:46,110 --> 00:06:47,870
do you know how much I'll lose?

117
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:59,570
Xiao Xiao, since you mention this,

118
00:06:59,659 --> 00:07:01,420
let's talk about it.

119
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:03,490
[File pocket]

120
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:07,600
Look at these.

121
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,610
All these papers have the records

122
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:12,050
of the company giving
you the full resources

123
00:07:12,050 --> 00:07:17,020
in order for you to become
the head broadcaster.

124
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:19,200
Now you want to leave us,

125
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,660
what's that supposed to mean?

126
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,730
Mr Chen.

127
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:26,090
I wish I could ride out
the storm with you.

128
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:28,290
I have my son to think about.

129
00:07:29,090 --> 00:07:30,540
There're endless expenses.

130
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:31,740
My subsidised salary

131
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:33,330
is hardly enough to feed my kid.

132
00:07:33,330 --> 00:07:37,280
I've signed quite a few
baby product contracts.

133
00:07:37,370 --> 00:07:38,780
If we stop for three months,

134
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:41,550
the termination fee will be astronomical.

135
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,700
I could bring over my contracts

136
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:45,400
in a new company.

137
00:07:45,490 --> 00:07:47,420
It'll lessen your burden this way.

138
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:53,600
Since you disregard our work relationship,

139
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:57,780
then let's talk about your
contract termination fee.

140
00:07:57,780 --> 00:07:59,630
How do you plan to pay me the fee?

141
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,820
Rest assured,

142
00:08:00,910 --> 00:08:03,840
the legal person from my
new company will talk to you.

143
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,830
Are you kidding me?

144
00:08:32,850 --> 00:08:34,220
[Jiang Zhe Yang Private Label
Concept Release Special]

145
00:08:34,299 --> 00:08:35,700
[Vine]

146
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:43,110
Hello, everyone. It's been a long time.

147
00:08:43,110 --> 00:08:46,280
Today Mr Five and I have an announcement.

148
00:08:47,290 --> 00:08:48,600
Mr Five.

149
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:50,900
Hello, everyone. I'm Mr Five.

150
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:53,370
We had some problems

151
00:08:53,450 --> 00:08:55,640
during our last program.

152
00:08:55,730 --> 00:08:57,560
Today we're making a clarification.

153
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,650
This is the patent

154
00:08:58,730 --> 00:09:00,760
for the Vine Series that's awarded

155
00:09:00,850 --> 00:09:02,310
by the government.

156
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:04,330
[We didn't copy from anyone else.]

157
00:09:04,490 --> 00:09:05,630
[The Vine Series]

158
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:08,370
[was built on Mr Five's]

159
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:10,190
[previous work that includes]

160
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,440
[the denim elements.]

161
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,540
[Right, Mr Five?]

162
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,340
[That's right, just as she said...]

163
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:15,660
Timing's perfect this time.

164
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:17,500
Our dear fans

165
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:18,900
can pay attention

166
00:09:18,990 --> 00:09:20,460
to Mr Five's work.

167
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:22,260
Let's take a look at
what I'm wearing today.

168
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:25,280
It's one of the designs
from the Vine Series.

169
00:09:25,370 --> 00:09:27,200
It's a sweatshirt and
I feel comfortable wearing it.

170
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,330
[And it's made of cotton linen.]

171
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,950
[Is this the latest style?]

172
00:09:29,410 --> 00:09:32,410
Luckily, we manage to do
this just before the New Year.

173
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:34,720
Thank goodness.

174
00:09:35,070 --> 00:09:37,750
We have to thank Jia Yun for this.

175
00:09:38,020 --> 00:09:40,030
I wonder whether it was his conscience

176
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:43,070
or gratitude that made Chen Lang
give us the patent.

177
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:46,350
I just hope Chen Lang

178
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,290
can get Cloud Live

179
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:52,300
back on the right path.

180
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:55,030
I heard Xiao Xiao is
going to leave Cloud Live.

181
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,490
Many of them, too.

182
00:09:56,580 --> 00:09:58,670
Not sure if he's able
to weather the storm.

183
00:09:58,670 --> 00:10:00,130
Anyway, this is business.

184
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,210
When things are fine, we're galloping.

185
00:10:02,210 --> 00:10:03,620
When things are going south,

186
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:05,880
we'll see a stampede within the company.

187
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:09,960
Don't just look at the negative side.

188
00:10:10,530 --> 00:10:13,650
This incident may be a nuisance,

189
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:16,820
but it has put our company
in the spotlight.

190
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:19,460
The key is pre-sales strategy.

191
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:21,490
First, we must act fast.

192
00:10:21,570 --> 00:10:24,790
We should go all out for sale while
we're still hot from the incident.

193
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:27,240
Second, we must focus
on our target market.

194
00:10:27,330 --> 00:10:28,770
After every sale,

195
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:32,260
we need to do a data collection
and analysis on the customers.

196
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:35,140
We must get our after-sale services right.

197
00:10:36,930 --> 00:10:38,160
I agree.

198
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,950
[Rui Live]

199
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:49,280
I haven't got time to tidy up.

200
00:10:51,990 --> 00:10:53,340
I'm sorry.

201
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:55,590
Feel free to sit.

202
00:11:03,130 --> 00:11:05,880
Didn't expect you could
become like this, Mr Chen.

203
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:07,680
Now you're living in the office.

204
00:11:08,210 --> 00:11:09,890
It's good living here.

205
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:13,370
It's better than living on a farm
with the animals.

206
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:15,520
When I was a kid,

207
00:11:15,610 --> 00:11:17,940
I had to live above a pigsty.

208
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:19,080
Both floors were connected.

209
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,410
Bet you haven't seen it.

210
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:24,280
Didn't expect you were that poor.

211
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:26,520
No wonder you are overcautious.

212
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:28,590
Mr Duan Jr is more daring instead.

213
00:11:29,930 --> 00:11:32,000
Am I as you said?

214
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:36,400
If that's the case, then you're a snob.

215
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:39,870
I used to hear that whenever
you encountered difficulties,

216
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,020
Mr Duan Sr was always there for you.

217
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:43,260
And that was what he got for helping you.

218
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:45,060
Do you know what you've
done to Duan Ran and Xi Xi?

219
00:11:45,060 --> 00:11:47,180
I owe them nothing.

220
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:49,340
It was Duan Sheng Yun who started it.

221
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:53,490
Why am I telling you this?

222
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:57,280
But you.

223
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,980
Little Duckling is
your close friend, right?

224
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:02,400
Didn't you use her as well?

225
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:04,310
I think you're the most wicked.

226
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,780
I just couldn't help it.

227
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:10,070
I had a bad role model
and made a wrong decision.

228
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:12,600
There's no turning back for me.

229
00:12:14,450 --> 00:12:16,870
Who doesn't make a mistake?

230
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:22,030
If you don't owe Duan Sheng Yun,
then I don't owe you either.

231
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:24,410
We've reached a consensus on this.

232
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,780
You're free to leave if you want.

233
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:32,070
You can see it.

234
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:36,920
Nevertheless,

235
00:12:38,850 --> 00:12:40,980
I hope you can still bear with me, Cola.

236
00:12:42,740 --> 00:12:45,000
But now Cloud isn't
as good as it once was.

237
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:46,990
Even so,

238
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,420
I hope you can trust me as you once were.

239
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:51,880
Trust me this time.

240
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,270
Sure.

241
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,160
Well,

242
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:04,810
just tidy up your place.

243
00:13:04,900 --> 00:13:06,880
You'll feel better this way.

244
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:21,730
Mr Chen.

245
00:13:24,530 --> 00:13:27,590
Nobody could have expected
things would turn out like this.

246
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:29,700
They threatened me with
the company. I was scared.

247
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:30,940
I'm to be blamed.

248
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,170
It's my fault.

249
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:34,190
I'm to be blamed.

250
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:36,100
I'm to be blamed.

251
00:13:36,180 --> 00:13:37,280
Enough.

252
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:42,610
It was not entirely your doing.

253
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,640
Jia Yun was right to scold me.

254
00:13:46,850 --> 00:13:48,280
Look what I've done

255
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:51,090
to get to where I am.

256
00:14:30,010 --> 00:14:32,030
[Rolling in it]

257
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:35,160
[Blessing]

258
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:58,810
Babes,

259
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:02,220
Su Su seems to be in a good mood today.

260
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:03,980
Get ready, everyone.

261
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,250
Roger.

262
00:15:06,340 --> 00:15:08,230
I'll get prepared right away.

263
00:15:09,990 --> 00:15:11,350
Hello dear.

264
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,090
We need to put up the "blessing" sticker.

265
00:15:15,090 --> 00:15:16,360
Can you help us?

266
00:15:16,450 --> 00:15:17,420
-Sure.
-Not done yet.

267
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:18,480
Thanks.

268
00:15:18,570 --> 00:15:20,900
Why are you so superstitious now?

269
00:15:20,990 --> 00:15:23,870
Let's create a new
atmosphere for the New Year.

270
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:26,340
You think it's going to bring world peace

271
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:28,050
or fulfill our wishes?

272
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,900
Look at these red packets.

273
00:15:39,610 --> 00:15:42,250
[Yu Shi loves Su Su]

274
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:55,840
Jia Yun.

275
00:15:58,460 --> 00:16:00,120
There're so many red packets.

276
00:16:01,690 --> 00:16:03,050
Su Su.

277
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:04,470
Well,

278
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:06,220
you're early today.

279
