348
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,250
Where's Xi Xi?

349
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:04,340
She went to a shop that's
all the rage on the internet

350
00:19:04,340 --> 00:19:06,720
to get something for the Weiya Festival.

351
00:19:06,810 --> 00:19:08,080
She won't be long.

352
00:19:08,810 --> 00:19:09,950
Jia Yun.

353
00:19:10,140 --> 00:19:13,040
Is he ready for his mission?

354
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:14,590
Don't mention it.

355
00:19:14,610 --> 00:19:16,650
