the door in the toilet.]

363
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:50,310
Yu Shi.

364
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,090
Mr Duan.

365
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,210
Are you in there?

366
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:55,290
