369
00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,460
I'm just curious.

370
00:20:00,750 --> 00:20:02,980
Stop kidding, Mr Duan.

371
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:05,010
I have no idea.

372
00:20:05,180 --> 00:20:07,430
