376
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:23,940
Hold it, Mr Duan.

377
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:27,040
-Don't do that.
-Why?

378
00:20:27,130 --> 00:20:28,600
If you do that,

379
00:20:28,690 --> 00:20:31,270
