382
00:20:34,630 --> 00:20:36,170
locked in the toilet.

383
00:20:36,260 --> 00:20:37,520
It's so embarrassing.

384
00:20:37,530 --> 00:20:38,750
What's there to be embarrassed about?

385
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:40,800
It's not your fault that you're
locked inside.

386
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:42,850
It's the toilet's fault.

387
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:45,510
I just feel embarrassed.

388
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:47,800
Great things don't come easy, you know.

389
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:50,840
This is no time for jokes.

390
00:20:50,930 --> 00:20:52,990
I'm about to confess to Su Su.

391
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:55,040
I finally mustered my courage,

392
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:57,070
and now I'm stuck in the toilet.

393
00:20:57,710 --> 00:20:59,860
Why am I so unlucky?

394
00:21:00,050 --> 00:21:02,250
Why don't you confess

395
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:03,750
through the door?

396
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:05,140
Mr Duan.

397
00:21:05,530 --> 00:21:07,970
I don't think today
is a good time for this.

398
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:09,580
Today is the best day for this.

399
00:21:09,580 --> 00:21:10,990
You can forget about doing it,
if you miss it today.

400
00:21:10,990 --> 00:21:12,750
I've checked the lunar calendar.

401
00:21:12,750 --> 00:21:14,730
You sure will succeed if you do it today.

402
00:21:14,730 --> 00:21:16,430
-Okay.
-I'm locked in the toilet.

403
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:18,230
Today can't be a good day.

404
00:21:19,450 --> 00:21:21,480
What are you doing, Mr Duan?

405
00:21:21,570 --> 00:21:24,030
-Yu Shi, calm down.
-I'm listening.

406
00:21:24,230 --> 00:21:26,960
-Okay.
-It's time to open your heart.

407
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,900
Come on.

408
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,070
Duan Ran.

409
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:32,930
Why is he locked inside?

410
00:21:33,860 --> 00:21:35,140
The men's room?

411
00:21:39,470 --> 00:21:40,750
Can't unlock it?

412
00:21:41,450 --> 00:21:42,410
You can try.

413
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,310
I'll do it. Step aside.

414
00:21:44,580 --> 00:21:45,850
Is that you, Ms Qian?

415
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:47,660
I'm here to save you, Yu Shi.

416
00:21:48,060 --> 00:21:49,210
Ms Qian.

417
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,360
Ms Qian.

418
00:21:58,390 --> 00:22:00,200
Even Mr Duan couldn't unlock it.

419
00:22:00,370 --> 00:22:02,250
Are you all right?

420
00:22:02,340 --> 00:22:04,630
I'm not at all.

421
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:06,430
I'm giving up.

422
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:08,910
Just calm down.

423
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:11,460
Any idea, Duan Ran?

424
00:22:11,550 --> 00:22:13,950
I would have already
unlocked it if I could.

425
00:22:14,940 --> 00:22:16,210
Just calm down.

426
00:22:16,300 --> 00:22:17,960
We'll come up with something.

427
00:22:22,330 --> 00:22:23,650
What's going on?

428
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:25,580
Su Su is here.

429
00:22:29,100 --> 00:22:30,910
You need to queue up.

430
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,230
I'm queuing up.

431
00:22:33,610 --> 00:22:35,140
This is the men's room.

432
00:22:35,230 --> 00:22:36,630
I'm keeping him company.

433
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:39,070
Stop hiding from me. I already know it.

434
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:41,020
I saw the light sign this morning.

435
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:47,730
We wanted to give you a
surprise, but never expect

436
00:22:47,730 --> 00:22:49,400
this mishap could happen.

437
00:22:50,420 --> 00:22:51,700
Let me talk to him.

438
00:22:51,810 --> 00:22:53,000
Go ahead.

439
00:22:58,770 --> 00:23:00,040
Yu Shi.

440
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,750
Su Su.

441
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,300
Is that you?

442
00:23:04,390 --> 00:23:05,500
-Yes.
-Getting emotional.

443
00:23:05,500 --> 00:23:06,730
You're here, too.

444
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,340
I'm going to die of embarrassment.

445
00:23:09,340 --> 00:23:11,480
I'm sorry.

446
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:12,800
I'm sorry.

447
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:15,860
Are you feeling sorry for not
having the guts to confess to me,

448
00:23:15,860 --> 00:23:18,590
or being so stupid to
lock yourself in the toilet?

449
00:23:22,740 --> 00:23:24,760
You already knew it.

450
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:27,590
I'm truly sorry.

451
00:23:27,770 --> 00:23:30,050
I wanted to give you a surprise.

452
00:23:30,260 --> 00:23:32,520
I just couldn't figure it out

453
00:23:32,610 --> 00:23:35,550
why the toilet locked me inside.

454
00:23:35,730 --> 00:23:38,230
It's so embarrassing.

455
00:23:38,320 --> 00:23:39,610
I'm sorry, Su Su.

456
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:41,090
It was my fault.

457
00:23:41,180 --> 00:23:45,080
I've prepared a speech.

458
00:23:45,170 --> 00:23:48,260
