461
00:23:54,870 --> 00:23:57,200
But I can't remember a word now.

462
00:23:58,340 --> 00:23:59,660
Su Su.

463
00:24:00,120 --> 00:24:01,330
I really

464
00:24:01,420 --> 00:24:02,790
like you, Su Su.

465
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:04,440
I like you, Su Su.

466
00:24:04,530 --> 00:24:06,080
I know.

467
00:24:06,170 --> 00:24:07,620
In my current situation,

468
00:24:07,710 --> 00:24:10,000
