00:24:42,250 --> 00:24:43,270
and kind of dumb.

481
00:24:43,360 --> 00:24:45,490
And possess many undesirable traits.

482
00:24:45,590 --> 00:24:47,000
However,

483
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:50,630
I'm willing to be your girlfriend.

484
00:24:53,730 --> 00:24:54,700
