-Are you fool?

498
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,190
Calm down, Yu Shi.

499
00:25:25,280 --> 00:25:27,020
Help is on the way.

500
00:25:27,100 --> 00:25:28,340
I'll just wait.

501
00:25:28,420 --> 00:25:29,490
I'm cool.

502
00:25:29,580 --> 00:25:30,680
I'm fine.

503
00:25:45,980 --> 00:25:47,210
Ms Zhang.

504
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:50,450
You're Chen Lang's assistant, right?

505
00:25:50,450 --> 00:25:51,340
That's right.

506
00:25:51,420 --> 00:25:52,600
What do you want?

507
00:25:52,690 --> 00:25:54,100
I've something to tell you.

508
00:25:54,100 --> 00:25:55,550
I've kept this for long.

509
00:25:55,770 --> 00:25:57,830
There's something I want to clarify.

510
00:25:57,840 --> 00:25:59,970
He didn't mix the leftover
stock with imitation goods.

511
00:25:59,970 --> 00:26:02,700
