locks himself in his office.

516
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:14,250
He's completely isolated
from everyone else.

517
00:26:14,250 --> 00:26:15,660
I've been with him for so many years.

518
00:26:15,660 --> 00:26:17,320
I'm really worried about him.

519
00:26:17,460 --> 00:26:19,750
Can you visit him if you’re free?

520
00:26:21,330 --> 00:26:23,360
