535
00:27:03,450 --> 00:27:04,940
The two of them.

536
00:27:06,430 --> 00:27:08,360
Yes, we're talking about you both.

537
00:27:08,510 --> 00:27:10,180
Today we celebrate Yu Shi's

538
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:12,240
successful confession!

539
00:27:12,330 --> 00:27:15,860
